    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to deliver power to the rear wheels via a variable M-differential lock. The engine exhibits crisp throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies (ITBs) and remains mechanically robust with recent VANOS adjustment and rod bearing inspection. The chassis integrity is maintained with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry performs as intended. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain is exceptionally tight, with no fluid leaks or timing chain noise, making it an ideal candidate for the purist seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
